{
  "stem": "20035.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you see that Hungary, as such, was an ally of Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And basically, Hungarians believed that our government is going to protect Hungary, as such, from any major damage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although they had a political party which was called the Arrow Cross party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Arrow Cross party was absolute Nazi, absolute pro-Hitler, absolute anti-- first of all, very, very anti-Semitic and anti-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, this party started to come, basically, to the surface, probably around the early 1940s.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Already the war, we knew about Anschluss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew about Germany occupying Austria.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that Germany occupied Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But somehow, somewhere, we felt-- beside of my father being a highly-decorated soldier from the First World War-- he was excluded from some basic Jewish laws.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Which basically didn't affect us, but affected him in a-- on a commercial sense.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the big change, the major changes came as the war was rolling around, in the 1942s and '43s.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were completely, completely under the influence of-- and the propaganda of the-- of the-- of the Nazis of the-- the Germans, basically, and the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had-- my father bought and my brother-in-law installed an antenna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were able to get BBC, which is a British Broadcasting Company, news in Hungarian twice a day, which was 100% against the law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If my father would have been caught listening to those news, it would have been-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know what was the penalty, but jail for sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was not allowed to have.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had a shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The radio was in our bedroom and in the attic, we installed, in our house, an antenna, my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew enough, that's how to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
